    <h4>What is Anyfile Notepad</h4>
    <p>Anyfile Notepad is a Google Drive compatible app that let's you open any type of files on Google Drive. To get started simply open a file using the open with function on Google Drive or use the built-in file explorer in Anyfile Notepad to open a file. You can also create new files from the create menu in Google Drive.</p>
    
    <h4>How to open any type of files</h4>
    <p>Right now we are building the mime types database. If you cannot open a file with Anyfile Notepad directly in Google Drive use the file explorer at the left on the editor window. This mime type will be automatically sent to the 'To be added mime types' page and will be integrated shortly after.</p>
    
    <h4>Creating files</h4>
    <p>Simply open the Anyfile Notepad app in your Chrome apps. Note that new files are created with the mime type 'text/plain'</p>
