    <h4>Usual disclaimers...</h4>
    <p>Please note that we cannot be responsible of any file corruption (not that i want it to happen) or anything destroying your files. This app will never send a destroy command to any of your files but note that non UTF-8 files can be corrupted when used with this app (don't worry the app will also warn you before doing it)</p>
    <p>Please note that this program doesn't directly support non UTF-8 encoded documents (like PDF) but it is still possible to open them BUT on they will be saved as UTF-8 so editing these files is highly unrecommended.</p>
    <p>Also note that this application doesn't use https between the app and you. Your files are not encrypted.</p>
    
